concept.CONCEPT_NAME: Early onset parkinsonism and intellectual disability syndrome

ConceptSets.name: [ucepd][Pheb2023] ingredients that cause parkinsonism excluding those used for PD

InclusionRules.name: has at least 1 PD condition in PD concept set
has 2 encounters with PD code that are at least 30 days apart
has encounters with PD code across at least 4 years
has Parkinson's medication with duration >6 months
has no meds associated with parkinsonism
